<sect1 id="analysis_class_page_1analysis_intro">
<title>Introduction</title>
<para>The <ref refid="classanalysis" kindref="compound">analysis</ref> class is the central orchestrator for all physics analysis tasks in AnalysisG. It manages the complete workflow from data loading through model training to result evaluation.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="analysis_class_page_1analysis_inheritance">
<title>Inheritance</title>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classnotification" kindref="compound">notification</ref></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>└──┐</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>├──<sp/><ref refid="classanalysis" kindref="compound">analysis</ref></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>│</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classtools" kindref="compound">tools</ref><sp/>─┘</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>The analysis class inherits from:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>notification: For logging and progress reporting</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>tools: For utility functions</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="analysis_class_page_1analysis_lifecycle">
<title>Lifecycle</title>
<sect2 id="analysis_class_page_1analysis_construction">
<title>Construction</title>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="classanalysis" kindref="compound">analysis</ref><sp/>ana;</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>The constructor initializes all internal maps and prepares the analysis for configuration.</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="analysis_class_page_1analysis_configuration">
<title>Configuration Phase</title>
<para>Configure the analysis through <computeroutput>m_settings</computeroutput>:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a7142e8c027e12fc8b46e0045f733e107" kindref="member">m_settings</ref>.<ref refid="structsettings__t_1adfb471fcc454bdfb97309137a9c75d9e" kindref="member">output_path</ref><sp/>=<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;results/&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a7142e8c027e12fc8b46e0045f733e107" kindref="member">m_settings</ref>.<ref refid="structsettings__t_1a383cb4d94ff68571dc4cd2e8a9f4d00f" kindref="member">threads</ref><sp/>=<sp/>8;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a7142e8c027e12fc8b46e0045f733e107" kindref="member">m_settings</ref>.<ref refid="structsettings__t_1ab1ea0b6cb2fcc7c77af0424e55c39e1e" kindref="member">epochs</ref><sp/>=<sp/>100;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a7142e8c027e12fc8b46e0045f733e107" kindref="member">m_settings</ref>.<ref refid="structsettings__t_1a7e4a89f57124d740aee08c1dff380320" kindref="member">kfolds</ref><sp/>=<sp/>5;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a7142e8c027e12fc8b46e0045f733e107" kindref="member">m_settings</ref>.<ref refid="structsettings__t_1a574cb98d49f69c527eed1fe1c64e22a5" kindref="member">batch_size</ref><sp/>=<sp/>64;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a7142e8c027e12fc8b46e0045f733e107" kindref="member">m_settings</ref>.<ref refid="structsettings__t_1af8bf8b05ab282c3e253234cbc4fbca6a" kindref="member">train_size</ref><sp/>=<sp/>80;<sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>80%<sp/>training,<sp/>20%<sp/>testing</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="analysis_class_page_1analysis_setup">
<title>Setup Phase</title>
<para>Add samples and templates:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Add<sp/>data<sp/>samples</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1ad49ba744577bd6d17f83efa48909f767" kindref="member">add_samples</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;/data/ttbar/&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;ttbar&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1ad49ba744577bd6d17f83efa48909f767" kindref="member">add_samples</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;/data/background/&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;bkg&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Add<sp/>event<sp/>templates</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a6d71bcd8dfe9deb47acba686df1e0058" kindref="member">add_event_template</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">new</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>MyEvent(),<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;ttbar&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a6d71bcd8dfe9deb47acba686df1e0058" kindref="member">add_event_template</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">new</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>MyEvent(),<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;bkg&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Add<sp/>graph<sp/>templates</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a03e15b76f9271d2c98f094cd7cdb3863" kindref="member">add_graph_template</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">new</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>MyGraph(),<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;ttbar&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a03e15b76f9271d2c98f094cd7cdb3863" kindref="member">add_graph_template</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">new</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>MyGraph(),<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;bkg&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Add<sp/>selection<sp/>templates</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a4ef9fa88fc930b37691ed93602c4b24c" kindref="member">add_selection_template</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">new</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>DileptonSelection());</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Add<sp/>model<sp/>for<sp/>training</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="structoptimizer__params__t" kindref="compound">optimizer_params_t</ref><sp/>params;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">params.<ref refid="structoptimizer__params__t_1aeb08bcbf67a3e24d81ee691020d99a21" kindref="member">lr</ref><sp/>=<sp/>0.001;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a51e47012fc4522964dbfba5baa89090c" kindref="member">add_model</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">new</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>MyModel(),<sp/>&amp;params,<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;model_v1&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>Add<sp/>metrics</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a33de64cfd2bc244ff02feb0cc9b2db58" kindref="member">add_metric_template</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="keyword">new</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>AccuracyMetric(),<sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">new</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>MyModel());</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="analysis_class_page_1analysis_execution">
<title>Execution Phase</title>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="normal">ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a401745bb4bcae03160ffa0b5df2887e7" kindref="member">start</ref>();</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
<para>The <computeroutput>start()</computeroutput> method triggers the complete analysis pipeline:<orderedlist>
<listitem><para>Cache checking</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Project structure building</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Event processing</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Selection application</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="classGraph" kindref="compound">Graph</ref> construction</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Model training/inference</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Metric evaluation</para>
</listitem></orderedlist>
</para>
</sect2>
<sect2 id="analysis_class_page_1analysis_monitoring">
<title>Monitoring</title>
<para>Monitor progress during execution:</para>
<para><programlisting filename=".cpp"><codeline><highlight class="keywordflow">while</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>(!ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1aa9288840e05af08f88af73f6ceca8f29" kindref="member">is_complete</ref>()[</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;model_v1&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">])<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>prog<sp/>=<sp/>ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1ab550330c7c309f24423fa3d48481ea64" kindref="member">progress</ref>();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>mode<sp/>=<sp/>ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a14ff6c25448d59d0c6296c45ba180485" kindref="member">progress_mode</ref>();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight><highlight class="keyword">auto</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>report<sp/>=<sp/>ana.<ref refid="classanalysis_1a6b719e04f433468bc84c45aa31abb400" kindref="member">progress_report</ref>();</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::cout<sp/>&lt;&lt;<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;Model:<sp/>&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>&lt;&lt;<sp/>mode[</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;model_v1&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">]<sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>&lt;&lt;<sp/></highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;<sp/>Progress:<sp/>&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal"><sp/>&lt;&lt;<sp/>prog[</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;model_v1&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">][0]<sp/>&lt;&lt;<sp/>std::endl;</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>std::this_thread::sleep_for(std::chrono::seconds(5));</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting></para>
</sect2>
</sect1>
